The paper deals with the problem of visual descriptors retrieval, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The method proposed in the paper is based on k-means clustering, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also tests the method on large scale databases, which is a common topic in database systems (cs.DB).
